metadata.name: StandUpForUkraine #1
metadata.description: Stand Up for Ukraine charity event powered by MemeNFT, hosted by @FullyVoxxed and project leaders. MemeNFT officially partnered with Unchain.Fund to help displaced civilians within Ukraine. All proceeds generated through this event will be donated to Unchain.Fund to help provide humanitarian aid to Ukraine. Each mint will cost .01 ETH on a Low Gas Fee Smart Contract, and will have a 20% royalty fee on each sale on OpenSea which will also go to Unchain.Fund.
